data.description: $8K Seller Contribution Available. Don't Miss Your Chance!  Welcome to 22273 S 227th Way, a stunning 3 bedroom and 2.5 bath single level property nestled in the heart of Queen Creek, AZ 85142. This immaculate home offers the perfect blend of modern elegance and comfort, making it an ideal haven for those seeking a contemporary lifestyle. This beautiful residence boasts a spacious and well-designed spilt floor plan, featuring a formal dining room, formal living room, family room, den and 3 bay tandem garage. The interior is adorned with high-end finishes and thoughtful touches, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an abundance of natural light streaming through large windows, highlighting the seamless flow between the living spaces. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, equipped with top-of-the-line appliances, sleek countertops, and ample storage space. The master suite is a true retreat, offering a peaceful sanctuary with a luxurious ensuite bathroom and generous closet space, free standing tub & separate walk-in shower. The den transitions to two secondary bedrooms, ideal for little ones. Some of the amenities available include 220 power outlet in the 3 bay tandem garage for electric vehicle charging, tankless hot water heater & RV parking to just name a few. Located in a desirable community, this home provides easy access to shopping and growing downtown QC.  The neighborhood offers a sense of community and convenience, making it an excellent choice for families, professionals, and anyone looking to embrace a high-quality lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to make 22273 S 227th Way your new home. Come and experience the perfect blend of luxury and comfort in this exquisite Queen Creek property. Schedule a viewing today and make this dream home yours!
